lead_paragraph: France may have ousted rivals Germany for the first time in 58 years but it will mean nothing if they lose Sunday's Euro 2016 final against a Portugal team that have had more recovery time, said Didier Deschamps.

headline.print_headline: France Haven't Won Anything Yet, Says Focused Deschamps
